==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Momentary
<hw>Mo"men*ta*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>momentarius</ets>. See <er>Moment</er>.]</ety> <def>Done in a
moment; continuing only a moment; lasting a very short time; <as>as, a
<ex>momentary</ex> pang</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>This <qex>momentary</qex> joy breeds months of pain.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Momently</ent>⟦br⟧
